    "causal_summary": "Packet 030 designed a full v1.0.4 matrix but intentionally did not execute it. It chose per-feature runners plus a meta-aggregator, and it required non-applicable cells to be first-class results. This packet executes the available runner surface, freezes the feature x executor matrix, and records honest blockers where packet 030's design is not yet backed by runner code.",
